b'$OCA.U Mrs. Pantoya was also Vice President, Corporate Strategy and Development at Verizon where she led acquisition efforts for multi-billion dollars in assets, including the acquisition of AOL.'

b'$OCA.U Higgins also aligned with Jesse Derris to launch a brand strategy and communications firm that has represented a number of leading DTC brands, including Warby Parker, Harry\xe2\x80\x99s, Reformation and Everlane. and an early shareholder in many disruptive brand such as Hims.'

b'$OCA.U The agency has over 900 employees and is regarded as one of the top advisors to Fortune 500 companies on emerging marketing strategies before they go mainstream \xe2\x80\x94 including, for example, serving as the U.S. agency of record for TikTok'
b'$OCA.U Mr. Higgins has a deep lens into consumer trends through RSE\xe2\x80\x99s partnership with Gary Vaynerchuk in the leading digital-first marketing firm VaynerMedia.'
